## ESG Committee

The ESG Committee met four times in 2023.

An ad hoc ESG Committee was established in 2022 to monitor the development of ESG within ING. The ESG Committee has been established for an initial duration of two years. The SB is in the process of evaluating the functioning of the committee and whether the ad hoc character of the committee will be extended or made permanent.

